dialogue.introduction: Submarine RO500, formerly U-boat U-511. I'm Ro, formerly called Yuu! Admiral? I will be in your care
dialogue.library_intro: I'm RO-500, the Kriegsmarine U-boat U-511 remodeled for use by the Japanese Navy. I was operated from my home port of Maizuru. I may not have seen actual battle, but I did train hard with a counter-submarine fleet, yes!
dialogue.secretary2: Yes, my Japanese has improved. I tried my best. Yes!
dialogue.secretary3: Um... Admiral, that's not really a greeting is it? You can't do that, okay? Okay? Okay?
dialogue.secretaryidle: Practicing with submarine is okay but... Ro wanna do real battle too! Hey admiral...? Are you listening...? Uuu! You are not!
dialogue.secretarymarried: Admiral, Guten Tag...oh, this? I tried baking Stollen for Hacchan...want to try some? Yes♪
dialogue.wedding: Admiral, you called? What's this ring for...? D-Danke! Um that's wrong... thank you. Our honeymoon will be in Maizuru, right?
dialogue.show_players_score: Admiral, you want to see the report? Understood!
dialogue.equipment1: Danke... Wait that's not it... Thank you! I'm right this time right?
dialogue.equipment2: I'm happy desu te! Danke! Danke!
dialogue.docking_moderate_damage: It'd be nice if I could go to Maizuru's hot spring again. Admiral, I'd like it if you would take me there.
dialogue.ship_construction: A new ship girl has arrived!
dialogue.start_a_sortie: Submarine fleet, please follow Ro. Fleet, move ooooouuutt!
dialogue.battle_start: Enemy fleet sighted. Here I go. Fiiirreee!
dialogue.attack: Ro might not match Bismarck or Eugen... But Ro will do her best!
dialogue.night_battle: Night battle time! Ro will do her best garuru-
dialogue.night_attack: Fire, Fire! The oxygen torpedos are so powerful!
dialogue.artillery_spotting: Fire, Fire! The oxygen torpedos are so powerful!
dialogue.night_special_attack_modifier_cutin_at_n: Fire, Fire! The oxygen torpedos are so powerful!
dialogue.support_expedition_team_arrival: Fire, Fire! The oxygen torpedos are so powerful!
dialogue.mvp: Huh? Ro is number one? Danke desu tte! I'm going to boast to Hacchan!
dialogue.moderately_damaged: I've been hit! I'm still fine but... I want to go back!
dialogue.sunk: No... Nooo... It's cold... So cold... And dark...
dialogue.second_anniversary_2015: Admiral, you did it! Today is a festival right? Ro too, is happy! Yup!
dialogue.early_summer_2015: It's getting hotter. Admiral! You should change into your swimsuit. I wanna see it!
dialogue.midsummer_2015: The summer is coming! I will swim! Dobooooon! Dobooooon!! Shioi said that.
dialogue.christmas_2015: Merry Christmas! Admiral, this turkey is delicious.
dialogue.setsubun_2016: I heard it from Eugen. Today is an important cultural day called Setsubooom~!

hourly.0000: 00:00 Admiral,thanks for your hard work desu tte! Today Ro will be your secretary desu tte! I will be in your care!
hourly.0200: Admiral! It's 02:00 ! Huh... did I say it wrong...? Um... really? Uuu...
hourly.0300: 03:00 Admiral! I wonder if this time is okay...? It is? Okay then!
hourly.0400: 04:00 Admiral! Ro is sleepy... but Ro will do her best! Yes!
hourly.0500: 05:00 Admiral! Guten Morgen! Morning desu tte! Morning!
hourly.0600: 06:00 Everyone, wake up! Guten Morgen Guten Morgen
hourly.0700: 07:00 Admiral! What shall we eat for breakfast? Bread and cheese is fine? Then... let's ea~t!
hourly.0800: 08:00 Admiral! Huh? You're still hungry?　Ah... Ro is sorry admiral... Uuu...
hourly.0900: 09:00 Admiral! Ro promised to dive with the I class submarine! It's fun... Yes!
hourly.1000: 10:00 Ah... Hacchan! Yahoo~ Decchi and Iku too, Guten Morgen! Huh...? Decchi... why are you mad? Eh?
hourly.1100: 11:00 Admiral! It's fun diving with those I-class submarines! Yes!
hourly.1200: 12:00 What shall we eat for lunch Admiral? "When in trouble please find Mamiya"...? Okay then!
hourly.1300: 13:00 Mamiya's lunch was delicious. Even Bismarck feast on it... right?
hourly.1400: 14:00 Admiral! What shall we do this afternoon? Orel? Bashi? What shall we do? Right?
hourly.1500: 15:00 Max! Where are you going? *nod* *nod*... Take care!
hourly.1600: 16:00 Maruyu! Hey! Maruyu! Ah... Why are you running away? Hey... Maruyu!
hourly.1800: 18:00 It's dinner time admiral! What now what now... what shall we have?
hourly.1900: 19:00 What's that Lebe? Kaltes essen? Rye bread with sausage and ham? Looks delicious... what, I can have it!?
hourly.2000: 20:00 Lebe's dinner was delicious! Admiral, Ro is full too! Ehehe~
hourly.2100: 21:00 Admiral! What's that? It's not beer? Foam...? Uuu... it's hard to differentiate... looks like beer to Ro...
hourly.2200: 22:00 Admiral! How about some real German beer then?　After all, we have... well, there are none left...
hourly.2300: 23:00 Admiral! Thank for your hard work today! Let us do our best tomorrow! Gute Nacht.
